description.narrative: Combat international narcotics production and trafficking; reduce the cultivation and production of drugs; prevent the resurgence of drug production; and limit the public health effects of the drug trade through international drug control and demand reduction, prevention and treatment projects.

This award strives to combat international narcotics production and trafficking; reduce the cultivation and production of drugs; prevent the resurgence of drug production; and limit the public health effects of the drug trade trhough international drug control and demand reduction, prevention and treatment projects. More specifically, this includes PROG/DEV & SUPPORT - DOMESTIC. Interregional Aviation Support.
